news.title: Jaisalmer: 18 dilapidated houses in Sonar Fort razed
news.para: ​The administration said there was a possibility of damages to lives and properties in houses situated near the locked, dilapidated houses in the fort during heavy rains.

news.title: Kolkata: E-mutation for Rajarhat-Gopalpur properties soon
news.para: BMC MMiC Debraj Chakraborty said that e-mutation camps will be held for residents living in Rajarhat Gopalpur sideto help them with any of their queries.

news.title: Property possession hurdle for Pune civic body in 11 merged villages
news.para: The civic administration has got these properties on paper from the respective gram panchayats and the district administration.

news.title: Thrikkakara municipality council recommends cancellation of building permit
news.para: Meanwhile, the council approved the recommendation of the finance standing committee to issue notices to owners of buildings which were expanded without the permission of the local body and regularize it after collecting a fine amount.

news.title: HC restrains Chennai civic body from collecting hiked property tax
news.para: When the matter came up on July 25, the Corporation Standing Counsel circulated a Council resolution dated May 30, 2022 of the GCC, which was based on a GO dated March 30 this year, and a consequent notification dated April 11, 2022.

news.title: Expedite process for implementation of DDA's land pooling policy: Delhi LG
news.para: The statement said that the LG also gave instructions to dispose of the claims pending for payment of ex-gratia to families of Covid victims within 15 days.

news.title: Lucknow: Consumer forum direct Sushant Golf City's builder to slash maintenance charges
news.para: DCDR chairman Amar Jeet Tripathi and member Pratibha Singh gave the order on a petition by the resident welfare association (RWA) of the Sushant Golf City.

news.title: Noida: 1,400 flats to be evacuated for Supertech twin towers demolition
news.para: The twin towers, Apex and Ceyane, are flanked by other buildings of Supertech's Emerald Court on one side and ATS Greens Village on the other. Emerald Court has 660 flats and Greens Village has 736, all of which will have to be evacuated, affecting around 5,000 residents.

news.title: Cash expenses for flat improvement OK, says ITAT
news.para: Tax experts explain that unaccounted money was not used for such payments and as the taxpayer was not engaged in business, various restrictive provisions relating to payment in cash did not apply in this case.

news.title: YEIDA cancels land allotment for township over Rs 233 crore dues
news.para: The Yamuna Expressway Authority has cancelled the allotment of a 100-acre land for a residential project in Sector 18 over non-payment of Rs 233 crore dues and violation of other statutory terms.

news.title: Urban Infra VC Fund seeks cancellation of Lodha SOBO JV project's MahaRERA registration
news.para: The Urban Infrastructure Opportunities Fund (UIOF), part of the UIVCF, has filed a complaint alleging gross violations of the provisions of the Real Estate (Regulation and Development) Act, 2016 by real estate developers and partners Terraform Realty Group.

news.title: HomeFirst Finance's net profit rises 46% to Rs 51 crore in Q1 FY23
news.para: Total income grew by 19.4 per cent to Rs 169 crore in three months ended June of FY23. It was Rs 142 crore in same period of FY22, HomeFirst Finance said in a release.

news.title: Sebi clears change in ownership of HDFC Property Ventures
news.para: In April, HDFC Bank and its parent company Housing Development Finance Corporation (HDFC) got approvals from their respective boards for the proposed scheme of amalgamation.

news.title: Not authorised intermediary to collect money from Unitech buyers for providing updates: SC
news.para: The top court said the e-committee is already sending five lakh emails to litigants across the country free of cost and if 10 per cent of the homebuyers respond to his message, the lawyer would have collected almost Rs five crore.

news.title: China's Country Garden plans $360 million share sale to refinance debt
news.para: The transaction comes after a rally in property stocks earlier this week following reports Beijing plans a real estate fund worth up to $44 billion to help developers resolve a crippling debt crisis.
